text: Andrea Ruth Mitchell (7 February 1956 - 4 April 2020) was an Australian politician. She was a member of the Legislative Assembly of Western Australia from 2008 to 2017. She represented the seat of Kingsley. She was born in Brisbane. Mitchell was a member of the Liberal Party. Mitchell died on 4 April 2020 at the age of 64. ==References== Category:1956 births Category:2020 deaths Category:Politicians from Brisbane
